tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    duration_seconds INT,
    interactions INT
);

CREATE TABLE user_interface_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    feedback_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE WebsiteVisits (
    visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    visitor_ip VARCHAR(15),
    page_visited VARCHAR(255),
    time_spent_seconds INT
);

CREATE TABLE PageViews (
    page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_name VARCHAR(255),
    average_time_spent_seconds INT,
    total_views INT,
    bounce_rate DOUBLE
);

CREATE TABLE UserInteractions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    visit_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE website_visitors (
  visitor_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_name VARCHAR(50),
  visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  device_type VARCHAR(20),
  page_visited VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE page_views (
  view_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_id UUID,
  view_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  page_id UUID,
  time_spent_seconds INT
)

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
  interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_id UUID,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(20),
  interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_id UUID,
  feedback_type VARCHAR(20),
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE navigation_history (
  history_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_id UUID,
  page_id UUID,
  navigation_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)
